race.description: Road To Magic Millions Qtis 2YO Plate
race.comment: The babies kick us off with all but one of these facing the starter for the first time. LADY OF FIVE (3) was heavily supported at Eagle Farm on debut and didn't let backers down with an impressive one-length victory. Will have derived a stack of confidence from that win and can go right on with the job now. The well-bred I AM THAT GIRL (4) (dam was a Listed winner) is on debut but has shown ability at the trials and is sure to be well-educated out of the Gollan barn. Keep very safe. REMEMBRALL (8) placed in a recent Sunny Coast trial and Thompson stays on board for race day. In the mix. MAGRITTE (5) has shown enough in both trials to warrant some consideration in this contest. PIROUETTE GIRL (7) next in line.
